rooms.name: Little Safe Space
rooms.topic:
This text will appear unformatted on Element Desktop / Web.

If anyone receives any invites for these main rooms do not accept the rooms are as follows Rabbit Hole and Degeneracy

We, LSS (Little Safe Space), and all the littles and care givers that make up the little space community want to make it clear that pornography has no welcome in our community.
——————————————————————
Rules:
Just be yourself but be warned, ZERO TOLERANCE on 
~ Arguing
~ Illegal Postings
~ Harassing
~ Bullying
~ Spamming
~ Pornography of any sort
~ Cursing / Swearing
~ Anything sexual
~DDLG/MDLB/DDLB/MDLG (as these are sexual in nature).
Don't spread malware or deliberately break the room, clients and servers.
——————————————————————
Depending on the severity you may be banned if breaking these rules. 
Otherwise have fun.... if you're looking for a caregiver ask around, you might find a very good one. 

Message admins if you have any complaints.

The admins/mods are as follows:
Admin~CrystalLake,

Please be on good behavior. We hate to scold. Go on, have fun. And remember be good
